                            <comment id="15672635" author="stefania" created="Thu, 17 Nov 2016 03:57:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This patch will wrap all policies with &lt;tt&gt;TokenAwarePolicy&lt;/tt&gt;, even in the default case, making it explicit that cassandra-stress is using token aware routing.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The 3.0 branch is quite different and so I&apos;ve decided to limit this patch to 3.X+, unless objections. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The 3.X patch merges cleanly into trunk, and since cassandra-stress is quite similar in both branches, I&apos;ve decided to only run CI in 3.X.&lt;/p&gt;

